com.openxc.measurements
Interface Measurement

All Known Implementing Classes:
AcceleratorPedalPosition, BaseMeasurement, BrakePedalStatus, EngineSpeed, FineOdometer, FuelConsumed, FuelLevel, HeadlampStatus, HighBeamStatus, IgnitionStatus, Latitude, Longitude, Odometer, ParkingBrakeStatus, SteeringWheelAngle, TorqueAtTransmission, TransmissionGearPosition, TurnSignalStatus, VehicleButtonEvent, VehicleDoorStatus, VehicleSpeed, WindshieldWiperStatus
public interface Measurement

The Measurement is the base for all OpenXC measurements. A Measurement has at least a value and an age, and optionally a range of valid values.
